### Payment Tests
### Test payment processing and verification

@token = {{loginCustomer.response.body.accessToken}}
@orderId = {{createOrder.response.body.id}}

### 1. Process COD Payment
# @name processCOD
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/payments/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "method": "COD",
  "amountInt": 5998000000
}

### 2. Process SePay Payment
# @name processSePay
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/payments/process
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "method": "SePay",
  "amountInt": 5998000000
}

### 3. Verify Payment (Mock callback from gateway)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/payments/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "payload": {
    "status": "success",
    "transactionId": "TXN-123456789",
    "verified": true
  }
}

### 4. Get Payment by ID
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/payments/{{processCOD.response.body.paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Payment by Order ID
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/payments/order/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Verify Failed Payment
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/payments/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "payload": {
    "status": "failed",
    "errorCode": "INSUFFICIENT_FUNDS"
  }
}